# ============================================================
# DEPENDENCIES
# The node_modules folder contains all installed packages.
# It's never committed because it can be rebuilt from package.json
# using `npm install`. Committing it would bloat the repo massively.
# ============================================================
node_modules/

# ============================================================
# NEXT.JS BUILD OUTPUT
# .next/ is generated every time you run `npm run build` or `npm run dev`.
# out/ is generated when you export a static site.
# Neither should be committed — they're build artifacts, not source code.
# ============================================================
.next/
out/

# ============================================================
# ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES
# .env files contain secrets (API keys, tokens, credentials).
# These must NEVER be committed to git — if pushed to GitHub,
# they become publicly visible and can be exploited.
# Use .env.example (without real values) to document what's needed.
# ============================================================
.env
.env.local
.env.development
.env.production

# ============================================================
# CLAUDE CODE & SUPERPOWERS
# .claude/ contains Claude Code's internal state and memory.
# .claude/agents/ is unignored below — agent definitions are project
# source of truth and should be tracked.
# .superpowers/ contains skill definitions for the Claude Code harness.
# These are tool-specific config files, not project source code.
# ============================================================
.claude/*
!.claude/agents/
!.claude/agents/**
.superpowers/

# ============================================================
# OS & EDITOR ARTIFACTS
# .DS_Store is a hidden macOS folder metadata file — irrelevant on other systems.
# *.log files are runtime logs that should not be tracked in version control.
# tsconfig.tsbuildinfo is a TypeScript incremental build cache file.
# ============================================================
.DS_Store
*.log
tsconfig.tsbuildinfo

# Large media files — keep local only
*.mp4
